<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n25076f"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n25" href="#n25076f">N25 (VI.B.15)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n25all.htm#n25076f"> 76(f)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Pat (12) sent to Mt / to find name</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">The Nez Perc&eacute;s obtain their names in several ways, one of the more curious being the <mark>sending of a child in his tenth or twelfth year to the mountains</mark>, where he fasts and watches for something to appear to him in a dream and <mark>give him a name</mark>. <small> Edward Clodd, <a name="ECTTT" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#ECTTT"><cite title="source">Tom Tit Tot</cite></a> (1898) 102</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Raphael transcription: <a name="c14045d" href="c14all.htm#c14045d">VI.C.14:045(d)</a> </mm></dd> </dd></dl>
